Package: verdifax
Type: Package
Title: Verdifax SDK and Reproducible-Research Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Verdifax", email = "team@verdifax.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R client for the Verdifax cryptographic attestation pipeline.
    Provides three primary capabilities for computational research
    reproducibility: (1) auto-capture of the current R environment
    fingerprint (R version, installed packages with versions, git
    commit SHA, platform, optional random seeds, Docker container ID);
    (2) attestation of payloads via the Verdifax /execute REST API
    with the captured environment bound into the audit bundle; and
    (3) determinism verification via /execute/verify-determinism,
    which runs the same payload twice and reports whether both
    invocations produced byte-identical canonical manifest hashes.
    Designed for researchers who want to attest computational results
    with the same cryptographic rigor that financial-services and AI
    governance customers receive.
